articles.title: Air Navigation System Resilience
articles.description:
How to measure resilience when there is no demand? 
Paper submitted to ICNS2022 studying ways to measure air navigation system
resilience when there is a drastic demand change.
articles.contents: This webpage is the work space for the ICNS2022 paper.
